features: NOT A VOLTAGE CONVERTER. Keep in mind that these adapters for Europe will not convert voltage from 220V to 110V or vice versa. It is compatible with 100-240V Dual Voltage devices and does NOT work on devices that support 110V/125V ONLY while overseas. ALWAYS check the voltage reading on your appliance before plugging them into this Europe outlet adapter.

US to Europe Plug Adapter. TROND power converter for Europe is compatible with most European countries such as Austria, Belgium, Croatia, Denmark, Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Iceland, Italy, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, Turkey, etc. Check the description for more country lists. NOT WORK in UK/Ireland/Scotland.

5 in 1 European Plug Adapter. It turns a type c socket into 2 grounded US outlets, 2 USB-A & 1 USB-C charging ports, which can easily charge your laptop, cellphone, tablet or smart watch simultaneously; Max capacity up to 2500W; Each USB port can intelligently identify your mobile device and seeks to maximize its charging speed (USB-A: 2.4A, USB-C: 3.0 A).

Compact Europe Cruise Travel Essentials. Measured at 3.52 x 1.73 x 1.42 inches, this Italy travel plug adapter fits easily into your luggage without taking up too much space or adding unnecessary weight; No cord and no surge protection make it easy to electrify your appliances on a cruise ship tour to Europe. A white light indicates proper connection to the outlet.

Good Non-blocking Design. You will like that each outlet is in different orientations to accept chunky adapters. 3-way type c plug adapter with USB fit snugly and precisely into European outlets, ensuring a secure connection without blocking switches or other sockets. A must have when heading to Europe. Leave one in your backpack and one in your luggage as a backup!
